item.description:
@Clawz_fury wrote:

You probably have the wrong coords.

Butbutbut, if the object is spawned server sided, and not through the cache, just go to the line where it is spawned on, and comment it out.

Example:

// makeGlobalObject(1,1,1,1); // ^^ Is how you comment out a line!
